metadata.name: The magic of black and white photo
metadata.description:
I love black and white photos, they are graphic and minimalistic, but at the same time can perfectly convey the character's mood.

This photo was taken a few years ago, it was my first photo shoot. I wanted to see a new side of myself. I wanted to feel beautiful, after the difficult breakup with my boyfriend. I looked at the world with apprehension, but at the same time I had hope and faith in a happy future. And so it happened...

Photographer Ekaterina Predeina  
2835x4279 px  
1/1
